</ul>

<p>Clues:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Participant 07 moves quietly but notices everything.</li>
    <li>Red doors hide secrets that were never meant to be found.</li>
    <li>Some messages are hidden in the source of the pages.</li>
</ul>

